<br>
Why is this?<br>
<br>
Well, lets think about it now, using how I RP as a example, I guess.<br>
<br>
Of course, Shintou kills anything that isn't Evil. That is to say, its basically bound by racial/Religous/Class lines, the specifics of such isn't really important. Such things are really destined to fail, and it didn't really dawn upon me why I was failing at getting Shintou to the skill level that I throught he should be for complete overlord slaughter of everything that moved in Norrath.<br>
<br>
Why? Because Genocidal socities are destined to fail. Look at Real life. The Nazi's got their shit waxed. Those countries that are learning (I say learning 'cause total and complete acceptance of all peoples just isn't there yet in the world) to accept all people reguardless of race/religion/creed what have you are the ones that are successful. I'm not gonna list examples, just take a look at the world and you'll see, those countries that have Intolerance aren't really that good, where the ones with tolerance are that good.<br>
<br>
Now, lets slap this on EQ.<br>
<br>
The guild that isn't tolerant will never be able to raid better then the guild that is tolerant. Why? If you're asking that, read the above paragraph again thx.<br>
<br>
Same thing, when all peoples come together it just works better. When you don't tolerate, it just doesn't. <br>
<br>
As for RP or not, well. RP doesn't just have to be look a Darkelf and a Paladin hacking eachothers limps off everytime they cross paths, acceptable roleplay can be found in the drizzit style or whatever the hell you wanna call it.<br>
<br>
A problem of the Hardcore RPers (I myself included, I slip up and fuck up myself): Is that we see these guilds with all races/religions in them and automatically smack them with the Non RP Tag/RaidingGuild/Uberd00dfucktards whathave you. Wrong on our part.<br>
<br>
A Problem of the non Rpers. Not roleplaying. You got really no excuse not to be. Even Resolution and FnF on down, everyone can do it. Why aren't you. We're not asking for a 10000 page essay on how your character cut up a fire bettle. Read above. Everyone can RP. Just because you're a ShadowKnight of Innoruuk guilded with a Paladin follower of Nife, that doesn't mean its not RP, and its not entierly hard either. You can easily just toss off gods and hatred and say you're working together for the common good.<br>
<br>
Of course, you can't expect a &quot;Oh, well thats okay!&quot; answer from someone like Shintou or any of the other I guess I can use the term Religios Fanatics of Norrath. Just because we do this doesn't mean we're hammering your RP, we're just doing what we do. Roleplay. Take it personally at your own cost, not mine.<br>
<br>
Do I have anything else? Lemme see...<br>
<br>
You know what?<br>
<br>
That is all.<br>
<br>
