<br>
But you know, Im never so shitty that I dont leave the possability open for conversation.  Two of the most recent &quot;random&quot; RP'es I've had were with a wood elf and a froglok.<br>
<br>
Vabris loathes them, would rather kill them then look at them, but the RP was fun and when it was over there was a quick ooc exchange between us and that was that.<br>
<br>
RP is far from dead and FV is still the only server Ill play EQ on.<br>
<br>
To comment on what Shintou was saying, the people at the extreme suck ass.  I think that the people who use RP as an excuse to be an ass to someone are as detrimental to this server's health as the dyed-in-the-wool Doodz power-looterz.<br>
<br>
There is a happy medium, but I fear that some people will never reach it as it requires some work on their part.  I do my part by trying to get people involved with things RP wise and trying to coax the doodz into at least speaking in character.  I tend to get 1 out of 3, which isnt really a bad ratio considering.<br>
