Yes, the d00ds have increased. Yes, there's a significant group of people who play on the server for economic reasons. That doesn't mean the RP is dead. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.realitywerks.com/hosted-images/elludensig.png" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=fajon>Fajon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Warpriest<br>
